# Folder Structure

Follow `rules/folder-structure.md`:

- CSS -> `css/` (web)
- Scripts -> `script/`
- Types -> `types/` or `packages/shared/types/`
- React components -> `components/{feature}/`
- UI primitives -> `components/ui/`
- NestJS modules -> `modules/{name}/`
- Shared logic -> `packages/shared/` (never duplicate in apps)

Pages in `app/` must be thin wrappers — logic in hooks and feature components.
